graph TD
    SM[Self-Mod Goal<br/>Writes Code] --> WT[Worktree<br/>Isolation]
    WT --> B[Build + Test]
    B -->|Pass| D[Generate<br/>git diff]
    B -->|Fail| FX[Fix + Retry]

    D --> EV[Independent<br/>Evaluator LLM]

    EV -->|APPROVE| M[Merge to Main]
    EV -->|REJECT| FB[Feedback<br/>to Coder]
    FB --> SM

    M --> DP[Deploy]
    DP --> V[Post-Deploy<br/>Validation<br/>2h delay]

    style SM fill:#4a9eff,color:#fff
    style EV fill:#ff9f43,color:#fff
    style M fill:#2ecc71,color:#fff
    style FB fill:#e74c3c,color:#fff
